OL,3,CPrince George to attend Eton as he
OL,4,Cfollows in footsteps of William and
OL,5,CHarry
OL,7,FAdditional reporting by Royal Editor
OL,8,FChris Ship
OL,10,FKate and William's eldest son, Prince
OL,11,FGeorge, will attend the prestigious
OL,12,Fboarding school Eton College in
OL,13,FWindsor, Kensington Palace has
OL,14,Fannounced, following in the footsteps
OL,15,Fof his father and uncle.
OL,17,FIt is understood that Kate's former
OL,18,Fschool, Marlborough College, and some
OL,19,Fco-ed schools in North London were
OL,20,Famong the top private schools that
OL,21,Fwere considered for George.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
