OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781635704
OL,3,CPrince George to attend Eton as he
OL,4,Cfollows in footsteps of William and
OL,5,CHarry
OL,7,FBut it has been confirmed that George,
OL,8,Fwho is currently attending Lambrook
OL,9,FSchool in Berkshire, will now attend
OL,10,Fthe same school that King Charles and
OL,11,FPrincess Diana chose for their two
OL,12,Fsons, William and Harry, from
OL,13,FSeptember.
OL,15,FPrince William and Kate have been
OL,16,Ffiercely protective of their children
OL,17,Fas they attempt to give them as normal
OL,18,Fa childhood as possible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
