OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781635704
OL,3,CPrince George to attend Eton as he
OL,4,Cfollows in footsteps of William and
OL,5,CHarry
OL,7,FThey did allow cameras into Lambrook
OL,8,FPreparatory School when all three
OL,9,Fchildren began classes there in 2022,
OL,10,Fbut it was arranged with the minimal
OL,11,Fnumber of cameras and lenses possible.
OL,13,FPrincess Charlotte and Prince Louis
OL,14,Fwill continue to attend Lambrook,
OL,15,Fwhich is near the family's home,
OL,16,FForest Lodge, on the Windsor estate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
