OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781635704
OL,3,CPrince George to attend Eton as he
OL,4,Cfollows in footsteps of William and
OL,5,CHarry
OL,7,FThe Prince and Princess of Wales try
OL,8,Fto balance the inevitable interest in
OL,9,FPrince George as a future King and the
OL,10,Fneed for him to grow up without the
OL,11,Fkind of press intrusion William and
OL,12,FHarry endured in the 1980s and 1990s.
OL,14,FEton College is one of the UK's most
OL,15,Fprestigious schools, and its alumni
OL,16,Finclude many former prime ministers,
OL,17,Fincluding Boris Johnson and David
OL,18,FCameron.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
