OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781635704
OL,3,CPrince George to attend Eton as he
OL,4,Cfollows in footsteps of William and
OL,5,CHarry
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, a statement from the
OL,8,FWaleses said: "Kensington Palace can
OL,9,Fconfirm that Prince George will attend
OL,10,FEton College from this September."
OL,12,FHarry recently said sport was the one
OL,13,Fthing that kept him from quitting
OL,14,Fschool. In his memoir 'Spare,' the
OL,15,Fprince described his arrival at the
OL,16,Felite institution as a "profound
OL,17,Fshock".
OL,19,FAccording to Harry, William told him
OL,20,Fto "pretend you don't know me" at
OL,21,Fschool.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
